snippet.title: I Am Your President - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as another US president! Decide the fate of the world and run the country any way you like. Do you wish to start a war or make peace? Take care of the poorest or support capitalists? Advocate for gun rights or stand against them? It is all up to you!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/844980/I_Am_Your_President/
